quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  22,47,"Wọ́n sì ń kán ọ lójú fún ìyà náà. Allāhu kò sì níí yapa àdéhùn Rẹ̀. Dájúdájú ọjọ́ kan lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ dà bí ẹgbẹ̀rún ọdún nínú ohun tí ẹ̀ ń kà (ní òǹkà).<sup>1</sup>","[1] Fífa ọjọ́ kan gùn kò ní òpin, bí Allāhu bá ṣe fẹ́ ni. Nítorí náà, ọjọ́ kan lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu lè jẹ́ ẹgbẹ̀rún ọdún tiwa, ó sì lè jẹ́ ọ̀kẹ́ méjì ààbọ̀ (ẹgbẹ̀rún lọ́nà àádọ́ta) tiwa (50,000) tàbí jù bẹ́ẹ̀ lọ."
  22,48,"Mélòó mélòó nínú ìlú tí Mo lọ́ lára, tí wọ́n jẹ́ alábòsí. Lẹ́yìn náà, Mo gbá wọn mú. Ọ̀dọ̀ Mi sì ni àbọ̀ ẹ̀dá.",""
  22,49,"Sọ pé: “Ẹ̀yin ènìyàn, èmi mà ni olùkìlọ̀ pọ́nńbélé fún yín.”",""
  22,50,"Nítorí náà, àwọn tó bá gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n sì ṣe iṣẹ́ rere, àforíjìn àti arísìkí alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé ń bẹ fún wọn.",""
  22,51,"Àwọn tó ṣe iṣẹ́ (burúkú) nípa àwọn āyah Wa, tí wọ́n ń dá àwọn ènìyàn ní agara (láti tẹ̀lé àwọn āyah Wa, tí wọ́n sì lérò pé àwọn máa mórí bọ́ lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu); àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni èrò inú iná Jẹhīm.",""
  22,52,"A kò rán Òjíṣẹ́ kan tàbí Ànábì kan níṣẹ́ ṣíwájú rẹ àfi kí ó jẹ́ pé nígbà tí ó bá sọ̀rọ̀, aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n máa ju (n̄ǹkan) sínú ọ̀rọ̀ rẹ̀. Nítorí náà, Allāhu yóò pa ohun tí aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n ń jù sínú rẹ̀ rẹ́. Lẹ́yìn náà, Ó máa fi òdodo àwọn āyah Rẹ̀ rinlẹ̀. Allāhu sì ni Onímọ̀, Ọlọ́gbọ́n. <sup>1</sup>","[1] Āyah yìí ń fi rinlẹ̀ pé, kò sí ṣaetọ̄n kan tí ó lè gba āyah mọ́ Òjíṣẹ́ Allāhu lẹ́nu."
  22,53,"(Èyí ń ṣẹlẹ̀) nítorí kí (Allāhu) lè fi ohun tí aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n ń jù (sínú rẹ̀) ṣe àdánwò fún àwọn tí àìsàn ń bẹ nínú ọkàn wọn àti àwọn tí ọkàn wọn le. Dájúdájú àwọn alábòsí sì wà nínú ìyapa tó jìnnà (sí òdodo).",""
  22,54,"(Èyí ń ṣẹlẹ̀) nítorí kí àwọn tí A fún ní ìmọ̀ lè mọ̀ pé dájúdájú al-Ƙur’ān jẹ́ òdodo láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ. Nítorí náà, wọn yó sì gbàgbọ́ nínú rẹ̀, ọkàn wọn yó sì balẹ̀ sí i. Dájúdájú Allāhu l’Ó ń fi ẹsẹ̀ àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo rinlẹ̀ sójú ọ̀nà tààrà (’Islām).",""
  22,55,"Àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ kò sì níí yé wà nínú iyèméjì nípa rẹ̀ títí Àkókò náà yóò fi dé bá wọn ní òjijì tàbí (títí) ìyà ọjọ́ ìparun yóò fi dé bá wọn.",""
